Class GridGraph

java.lang.Object
com.group4.Auber.OperativeAI.GridGraph
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.badlogic.gdx.ai.pfa.Graph<GridNode>, com.badlogic.gdx.ai.pfa.indexed.IndexedGraph<GridNode>
public class GridGraph
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.badlogic.gdx.ai.pfa.indexed.IndexedGraph<GridNode>
Used to calculate how the operative needs to move by following the path. This is the main pathfinding class used by the Operative.
Author:
Adam Wiegrand
